'''以色列能源'''大部分來自[[化石燃料|化石燃料]]。[[一次能源|一次能源]]的總需求量遠高於總產量，嚴重依賴進口來滿足能源需求。2016年，一次能源的總消費量是{{convert|1.037|quad|TWh|abbr=on|lk=on}}或是26.2{{translink|en|tonne of oil equivalent|公噸油當量}}<ref name="eia" />。

2018年，有70%電力來自天然氣，4%來自可再生能源而其中有95%是太陽能光電系統<ref>[http://www.iea-pvps.org/index.php?id=6&eID=dam_frontend_push&docID=4827 PVPS annual report, 2018] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iea-pvps.org/index.php?id=6&eID=dam_frontend_push&docID=4827 |date=20190516193546 }}, p.72</ref>。可再生能源的供電量預計到2030年可達到30%<ref>Surkes, S. (2020) Cabinet greenlights target of 30% renewable energy by 2030, Times of Israel 25 October 2020, https://www.timesofisrael.com/cabinet-greenlights-target-of-30-renewable-energy-by-2030/ {{Wayback|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/cabinet-greenlights-target-of-30-renewable-energy-by-2030/ |date=20210531122317 }}</ref>。

